data.description: Welcome to 1335 Franklin Ave located in Collinsville IL. This 3 bedroom, 1 bath is move in ready and waiting for it's next owner. The large lot is almost half an acre and offers a lot of outdoor space to enjoy.  Whether it's sitting outside on the patio or relaxing on the deck, you will have plenty of room to relax or entertain. There is a carport located right outside the back door, offering coverage to carry in the groceries. Once you step inside you will be greeted with an eat in kitchen, all appliances included. The living room is bright and welcoming. 3 bedrooms and a bath round out the main floor of the home. As you head downstairs you will be happy to find a rec room with built in bar, adding more living space to this wonderful property.
